Package: PBAT
Title: Plant Breeding Analytical Tools (Shiny App)
Version: 0.1.0
Maintainer: Krishnan P Abhijith <abhijithkpgen@gmail.com>
Description: An interactive Shiny application for plant breeding analyses, including mating-design analytics (diallel, line x tester, partial diallel), ANOVA summaries, GCA/SCA effects, BLUE/BLUP utilities, PCA/plots, and exportable reports. Designed for non-programmers with a point-and-click interface.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/abhijithkpgen/PBAT
BugReports: https://github.com/abhijithkpgen/PBAT/issues
